                                </p>
                                <p class="text-muted mb-1">
                                    <i
                                        class="bx bx-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i>
                                    Understand the science behind perception and attention.
                                </p>
                                <p class="text-muted mb-1">
                                    <i
                                        class="bx bx-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i>
