                                </p>
                                <p class="text-muted mb-1">
                                    <i class="bx bx-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i>Understand the science behind perception and attention.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <div>
                                <button
                                    type="button"
                                    class="btn btn-danger me-2">
